      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUST BELIEVE (3) finished a 3.5 lengths third last start over 400m at this track in a speedy 22.68. Expected to go close again if runs up to latest time. STAR REBEL (2) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (22.77) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. The form out of last race has been strong. Likely to play a prominent role. PAW JELANI (1) shapes well for this on her excellent win a few runs back, getting around Horsham over 410m in 23.15 then hitting the frame in both runs since. Has the ability and can find winning form again. NO BAD DEED (8) has ability and can find the frame.",
